node.text: What can a @rhinocuttingsystems plasma table do? It can help you create anything you need for your next fabrication job. From custom suspension, to skid plates, badass light bar mounts, create mounting solutions for a 6x6, and so much more! If you’re looking to step up your fabrication game, be sure to check out @rhinocuttingsystems
